      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector, boasting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in showroom state. Mechanically peerless and meticulously preserved, it offers an uncompromised driving experience. This is an investment-grade acquisition for those who demand nothing less than perfection.",
