    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty in person to really believe it. It's in absolutely stunning shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! I've babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message, I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 44500.0,
