    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is mechanically pristine: the rod bearing service and VANOS solenoid overhaul are documented, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission to a limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with refreshed bushings, ensuring the sharp turn-in and telepathic feedback these chassis are renowned for. Zero oxidation on the undercarriage and a flawless interior make this a turn-key investment for the serious driver.",
